reviewText: Hate to give such a low review, but the copy I received was not an all region copy. It would not play in my Blu Ray player stating it was region locked.(I'm in the U.S.)

Collect all of  Doctors . This is the latest and I enjoy it. Peter is a different Doctor and I appreciate his take it is refreshing. This set is the British made version so it will not play on a regular Blue Ray player only a Multiregional Blue Ray will do.
